name: HdrHistogram.Net
body:
HdrHistogram.NET
================

A .NET port of [HdrHistogram](https://github.com/HdrHistogram/HdrHistogram), thanks to [Gil Tene](https://github.com/giltene)

###### Code is (deliberately) a line-by-line port, so it's isn't idiomatic .NET code!

##### Code ported so far
* All Histograms (long, short & regular)
* Iterators (using IEnumerable instead of Java iterators)
* All functional and performance tests

##### Still to do
* Serialisation/deserialisaion code
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
